        <h1 class="header center teal-text text-lighten-2">Random Number Generator</h1>
        <div class="row center">
          <a href="https://github.com/adeepkit01/RNG" id="download-button" class="btn-large waves-effect waves-light teal lighten-1">Check Out the Code</a>
